reviews.text: The McDonald's in sceneway garden was the worst McDonald's I ever seen. Always give me the wrong items. And the food quality is not good.

Having swum 1000 meters in a public swimming pool, I needed food and drink to revitalize myself. Remembering my wife’s advice about McDonald’s bargain offer today, I stopped by and got a set. I had no problem in finding a seat and ate in, overhearing nearby schoolgirls’ perspectives...
This Mc Donald's is the biggest in the area. Great if you want to find available seating.
